00:40:34,760 --> 00:40:36,910
But today, your reckless words

853
00:40:37,280 --> 00:40:39,610
will cause everyone in the village to die!

854
00:40:40,060 --> 00:40:40,760
Niwei,

855
00:40:41,080 --> 00:40:42,080
you're not my brother.

856
00:40:42,080 --> 00:40:43,030
I'm going to kill you!

857
00:40:43,030 --> 00:40:43,710
Meiwei!

858
00:40:44,850 --> 00:40:45,310
Meiwei!

859
00:40:45,320 --> 00:40:45,760
I...

860
00:40:46,440 --> 00:40:47,680
I'll shoot you right now,

861
00:40:47,680 --> 00:40:49,150
you disloyal bastard.

862
00:40:49,840 --> 00:40:50,920
Feng Niwei, are you crazy?

863
00:40:50,920 --> 00:40:52,120
He's your brother!

864
00:40:54,300 --> 00:40:55,300
I'm not crazy!

865
00:40:57,400 --> 00:40:59,210
My father died because of you!

866
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,630
You also starved my mother to death!

867
00:41:01,630 --> 00:41:03,030
Have you all forgotten?

868
00:41:04,310 --> 00:41:05,790
Each one of you is to blame

869
00:41:07,050 --> 00:41:08,610
for my parents' deaths!

870
00:41:09,690 --> 00:41:10,440
Father!

871
00:41:11,400 --> 00:41:12,110
Mother!

872
00:41:12,410 --> 00:41:14,010
If you can see us from heaven,

873
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:15,520
just witness this!

874
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:19,930
Today, I, Little Niwei,
will get justice for you!

875
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,280
Feng Niwei!

876
00:41:22,550 --> 00:41:23,760
Don't do evil!

877
00:41:23,810 --> 00:41:24,970
Your father's death

878
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,740
had nothing to do with the villagers.

879
00:41:26,740 --> 00:41:28,400
Don't end up like your father!

880
00:41:28,400 --> 00:41:30,320
How dare you mention my father?

881
00:41:36,400 --> 00:41:37,550
Shut your mouth!

882
00:41:37,570 --> 00:41:40,050
Chief!

883
00:41:41,000 --> 00:41:41,720
Chief!

884
00:41:44,080 --> 00:41:45,170
Kill him!

885
00:41:45,990 --> 00:41:46,760
Yes, sir.

886
00:41:52,570 --> 00:41:54,830
Feng Niwei, you've gone completely mad.

887
00:41:56,230 --> 00:41:57,030
Second Uncle!

888
00:41:57,590 --> 00:41:58,380
Second Uncle!

889
00:41:58,380 --> 00:41:59,490
Father!

890
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:01,150
Chief!

891
00:42:05,110 --> 00:42:06,390
Father!

892
00:42:07,670 --> 00:42:08,360
Feng Niwei,

893
00:42:09,560 --> 00:42:12,820
your father led bandits
to massacre our village back then.

894
00:42:13,660 --> 00:42:14,700
You're even worse

895
00:42:15,470 --> 00:42:16,550
than your father,

896
00:42:17,190 --> 00:42:18,960
being a lackey for the Japanese!

897
00:42:18,960 --> 00:42:20,510
How dare you?

898
00:42:24,950 --> 00:42:26,760
Father!

899
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:31,720
I know where the grain is!

900
00:42:32,110 --> 00:42:33,510
I know!

901
00:42:33,530 --> 00:42:34,450
Old Man!

902
00:42:36,440 --> 00:42:37,720
You hateful wretch.

903
00:42:38,030 --> 00:42:40,560
You won't learn
until you're at death's door.

904
00:42:41,210 --> 00:42:42,070
Bring him over.

905
00:42:42,070 --> 00:42:42,910
Go! Quickly!

906
00:42:43,250 --> 00:42:44,000
Old Man.

907
00:42:46,510 --> 00:42:47,280
Old Man.

908
00:42:47,730 --> 00:42:48,560
Where is it?

909
00:42:49,750 --> 00:42:51,350
Where did you hide the grain?

910
00:42:51,470 --> 00:42:52,730
I have two conditions.

911
00:42:54,040 --> 00:42:54,730
First,

912
00:42:54,940 --> 00:42:56,800
release everyone in the village.

913
00:42:56,830 --> 00:42:57,350
Second,

914
00:42:57,740 --> 00:42:59,450
let me take my brother home.

915
00:43:02,150 --> 00:43:02,840
Father!

916
00:43:03,070 --> 00:43:04,800
How dare you bargain with me?